---
import StarlightPage from "@astrojs/starlight/components/StarlightPage.astro";
---

<StarlightPage
  frontmatter={{
    title: "Design",
    description: "Links into Warden's architectural decisions and long-form design notes.",
  }}
>
  <section class="design-page">
    <p class="eyebrow">Architecture notes</p>
    <h2>Why Warden is shaped this way</h2>
    <p>
      Warden's public surface is intentionally smaller than the internal design record. This page
      points curious readers to the source documents without turning the site into a second copy of
      the ADR archive.
    </p>

    <div class="link-grid">
      <a href="https://github.com/99Yash/warden/blob/main/decisions.md">
        <span>decisions.md</span>
        <strong>Architectural Decisions</strong>
        <p>Every accepted direction, rejection, caveat, and milestone boundary.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com/99Yash/warden/blob/main/vision.md">
        <span>vision.md</span>
        <strong>Thinking Framework</strong>
        <p>The original long-form analysis that predates the current milestone sequence.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com/99Yash/warden/blob/main/CONTEXT.md">
        <span>CONTEXT.md</span>
        <strong>Noun Glossary</strong>
        <p>The project vocabulary agents and future contributors should reuse.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</StarlightPage>
